name: Denver Indian Health and Family Services (DIHFS)
description: DIHFS is Denver's only Urban Indian Health Program, offering culturally appropriate primary care, dental care, behavioral health services, and assistance with health insurance enrollment for American Indian and Alaska Native individuals and families
